<bibRefCitation author="Deeming, J. C." box="[322,505,260,287]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" pagination="784 - 806" refId="ref27916" refString="Deeming, J. C. (2011) Order Diptera, family Chloropidae. In: van Harten A, editors. Arthropod Fauna of the United Arab Emirates, Volume 4, pp. 784 - 806. Dar Al-Ummah Printing, Publishing, Distribution and Advertising, Abu Dhabi, UAE. 816 pp." type="book chapter" year="2011">Deeming (2011)</bibRefCitation>
